{"tid":2293223,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"誠哥要去到出年先有運","createTime":"2020-11-20T05:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T12:45:28.000Z","uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"330f365e3f35c79658c30ee27893a3805b8c65fc","tid":2293223,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:53:22.000Z","msg":"最近發覺誠哥同我同日主，運勢可能同我差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢由今年 4 月就開始衰（日主出干），10 月就受剋得最嚴重，起碼要去到出年 1 月啲運先會真正好轉<br />\n<br />\n所以長和系都係建議大家出年先諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1406a49817e4b7c59f22c878d65cda4ffb5e4e","tid":2293223,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ef2ac46b178a06ab04fc8052d9e1b26d18ff2f","tid":2293223,"uid":56743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"你睇睇去到2022先講"},{"pid":"61a436f7c733afe6668275cb2dfeb43628d7bfb4","tid":2293223,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"庚金性格嘅人比較講義氣，所以相信佢好運返會益吓股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45368496b5a6d10f7c5d858148f775095dc3caa","tid":2293223,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"65ef2ac46b178a06ab04fc8052d9e1b26d18ff2f","tid":2293223,"uid":56743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"你睇睇去到2022先講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"但出年到佢大仔唔掂，真係唔知有冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc656fe81eec5847fff6bdf5f800dc51edccfb2a","tid":2293223,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:08:06.000Z","msg":"希望如此<br />\n不過誠哥頂到而家都算係咁<br />\n睇睇其他港股 插水式下跌<br />\nbtw我都係庚金人 舊年同今年做咩都係事事不如意<br />\n希望下年行大運<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4faf915d44331ce7f4f6b835c25ea03fa6a0441","tid":2293223,"uid":56743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f45368496b5a6d10f7c5d858148f775095dc3caa","tid":2293223,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"65ef2ac46b178a06ab04fc8052d9e1b26d18ff2f","tid":2293223,"uid":56743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"你睇睇去到2022先講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"但出年到佢大仔唔掂，真係唔知有冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"睇埋四大家族，睇睇有冇啟示<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2675a156cbffcb267cffa3c907828ebafc584e09","tid":2293223,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:06:02.000Z","msg":"長實幾時撈得底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d667c14a27d18ccca94dd2c4f116a97668b8943d","tid":2293223,"uid":72734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"好耐無見到你，近排搞咩"},{"pid":"7340316ebc554d3672316478fe1e50ad70e187c1","tid":2293223,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d667c14a27d18ccca94dd2c4f116a97668b8943d","tid":2293223,"uid":72734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"好耐無見到你，近排搞咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"自閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb23723c28682cdac9b8f54cea6160449e6a2baa","tid":2293223,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2675a156cbffcb267cffa3c907828ebafc584e09","tid":2293223,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:06:02.000Z","msg":"長實幾時撈得底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"如果跟誠哥嘅運嚟講而家買得，估值上都係<br />